        public B forJsonSchema(org.apache.flink.table.api.TableSchema jsonSchema)
        Sets the schema of the JSON-encoded Kafka messages. If not set, the JSON messages are decoded with the table schema.
        参数:
        jsonSchema - The schema of the JSON-encoded Kafka messages.
        返回:
        The builder.

      • withTableToJsonMapping

        public B withTableToJsonMapping(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> tableToJsonMapping)
        Sets a mapping from schema fields to fields of the JSON schema.

        A field mapping is required if the fields of produced tables should be named different than the fields of the JSON records. The key of the provided Map refers to the field of the table schema, the value to the field in the JSON schema.

        参数:
        tableToJsonMapping - A mapping from table schema fields to JSON schema fields.
        返回:
        The builder.

      • failOnMissingField

        public B failOnMissingField(boolean failOnMissingField)
        Sets flag whether to fail if a field is missing or not.
        参数:
        failOnMissingField - If set to true, the TableSource fails if a missing fields. If set to false, a missing field is set to null.
        返回:
        The builder.

      • getJsonSchema

        protected org.apache.flink.table.api.TableSchema getJsonSchema()

        返回:
        The JSON schema for the TableSource.
